criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  1) histologically confirmed high-grade osteosarcoma;

          -  2) initially treated in Musculoskeletal Tumor Center of Peking University People's
             Hospital, Xijing Hospital or The Second Hospital affiliated to Zhejiang Hospital;

          -  3) imaging evaluation should be available;

          -  4) completed neo-adjuvant chemotherapy and at least 8 cycles of adjuvant chemotherapy;

          -  5) expected to live longer than 3 months with Eastern Cooperative Oncology Group
             performance status of 0 or 1;

          -  6) acceptable hematologic, hepatic, and renal function.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  1) Patients who could not complete neo-adjuvant chemotherapy or at least 4-month
             adjuvant chemotherapy;

          -  2) lost to follow-up.
